World's Best Cat Litter
short_description: About this item NATURALLY SCENTED — A lightweight and naturally scented cat litter made with no fake scents or artificial perfumes. OUTSTANDING ODOR CONTROL — More cats shouldn’t mean more smells — keep your cats happy with a natural litter with long-lasting odor control. QUICK CLUMPING & EASY SCOOPING — Multiple cats can most often mean more clean up — but not with this fast-acting natural litter that requires no chiseling or scraping. LIGHTWEIGHT, 99% DUST FREE & FLUSHABLE - SEPTIC SAFE — Naturally free of silica dust, this lightweight cat litter offers low tracking and less mess — and is tested and proven flushable and safe for septic and sewer systems.
